T1  - The economic impact of recession announcements
AU  - Eggers, Andrew C.
AU  - Ellison, Martin
AU  - Lee, Sang Seok
JO  - Journal of Monetary Economics
VL  - 120
SP  - 40
EP  - 52
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2021/05/01/
